---
import { SparklesText } from "./SparklesText";
import Spotlight from "./Spotlight";
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-xl flex-col gap-8 px-4 py-14 md:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl">
          &lt;Sobre <SparklesText
            text="InspiraTEC/>"
            client:visible
            className="text-4xl md:text-5xl"
          />
        </h2>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4 text-xl leading-8 text-white/80">
        Únete a la <strong>Hackathon IA</strong> para la sostenibilidad y genera
        impacto positivo.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-white/80">
        La <strong>Hackathon PachaqTech 2024</strong> es una iniciativa diseñada
        para fomentar el desarrollo de soluciones tecnológicas innovadoras que utilicen
        la <strong>inteligencia artificial</strong> para abordar desafíos relacionados
        con la sostenibilidad. Durante el evento, los participantes tendrán 24 horas
        para conceptualizar, desarrollar y presentar una solución que integre <strong
          >IA</strong
        >
        de manera efectiva en escenarios del mundo real.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-white/80">
        Este evento se destaca por reunir a mentores de primer nivel,
        especialistas en IA generativa, automatización y plataformas en la nube,
        que trabajarán junto con los equipos para garantizar que las ideas no
        solo sean viables, sino también escalables. Los participantes podrán
        interactuar con empresas líderes en tecnología y presentar sus
        soluciones a un jurado compuesto por expertos del sector.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto grid w-full justify-center items-center grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4"
    >
      <Spotlight client:visible>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 flex justify-end items-end opacity-40 transform rotate-12"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="h-56 w-56"
            ><rect x="16" y="16" width="6" height="6" rx="1"></rect><rect
              x="2"
              y="16"
              width="6"
              height="6"
              rx="1"></rect><rect x="9" y="2" width="6" height="6" rx="1"
            ></rect><path d="M5 16v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h12a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3"
            ></path><path d="M12 12V8"></path></svg
          >
        </div>

        <div class="relative p-4 z-10">
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-8 tracking-widest text-black"
          >
            &lt;SOSTENIBILIDAD&gt;
          </h3>
        </div>
      </Spotlight>

      <Spotlight client:visible>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 flex justify-end items-end opacity-40 transform rotate-12"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-56 w-56"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-brain-circuit"
            ><path
              d="M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.997.125 4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 0 .556 6.588A4 4 0 1 0 12 18Z"
            ></path><path d="M9 13a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3-4"></path><path
              d="M6.003 5.125A3 3 0 0 0 6.401 6.5"></path><path
              d="M3.477 10.896a4 4 0 0 1 .585-.396"></path><path
              d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-1.967-.516"></path><path d="M12 13h4"
            ></path><path d="M12 18h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"></path><path d="M12 8h8"
            ></path><path d="M16 8V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2"></path><circle
              cx="16"
              cy="13"
              r=".5"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="3" r=".5"></circle><circle
              cx="20"
              cy="21"
              r=".5"></circle><circle cx="20" cy="8" r=".5"></circle></svg
          >
        </div>

        <div class="relative p-4 z-10">
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-8 tracking-widest text-black"
          >
            &lt;INTELIGENCIA ARTIFICIAL&gt;
          </h3>
        </div>
      </Spotlight>

      <Spotlight client:visible>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 flex opacity-40 justify-end items-end transform rotate-12"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-56 w-56"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-brain"
            ><path
              d="M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.997.125 4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 0 .556 6.588A4 4 0 1 0 12 18Z"
            ></path><path
              d="M12 5a3 3 0 1 1 5.997.125 4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 1-.556 6.588A4 4 0 1 1 12 18Z"
            ></path><path d="M15 13a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-3-4 4.5 4.5 0 0 1-3 4"
            ></path><path d="M17.599 6.5a3 3 0 0 0 .399-1.375"></path><path
              d="M6.003 5.125A3 3 0 0 0 6.401 6.5"></path><path
              d="M3.477 10.896a4 4 0 0 1 .585-.396"></path><path
              d="M19.938 10.5a4 4 0 0 1 .585.396"></path><path
              d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-1.967-.516"></path><path
              d="M19.967 17.484A4 4 0 0 1 18 18"></path></svg
          >
        </div>

        <div class="relative p-4 z-10">
          <h3
            class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-8 tracking-widest text-black"
          >
            &lt;CREATIVIDAD&gt;
          </h3>
        </div>
      </Spotlight>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex gap-4 flex-col md:flex-row">
        <a
          href="#"
          target="_blank"
          class="group uppercase ring-border-focus focus-visible:ring-offset-bg outline-none ring-0 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-background disabled:bg-bg-disabled disabled:text-fg-disabled inline-flex shrink-0 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-2xl text-lg font-medium leading-normal transition-colors disabled:cursor-default bg-brand2 hover:bg-brand2/80 active:bg-brand2/80 h-14 px-6 [&_svg]:size-4 text-black"
        >
          Descargar programa<svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-chevron-right ml-1 size-8 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-1"
            ><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="#"
          target="_blank"
          class="group uppercase ring-border-focus focus-visible:ring-offset-bg outline-none ring-0 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-background disabled:bg-bg-disabled disabled:text-fg-disabled inline-flex shrink-0 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-2xl text-lg font-medium leading-normal transition-colors disabled:cursor-default bg-brand2 hover:bg-brand2/80 active:bg-brand2/80 h-14 px-6 [&_svg]:size-4 text-black"
        >
          Descargar bases<svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-chevron-right ml-1 size-8 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-1"
            ><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
